race.comment: NITRO PLUME (4) hit the frame latest (30.18) when third at this track in a Restricted WIN. Looks suited here and rates on top. AYLA ZORRO (2) turned in a strong performance to win by a neck at Hobart over 461m (26.30) in a Grade 5. Sure to be thereabouts. BUCKLE UP MILES (7) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (30.47) at this track latest. Form at the trip sound including four wins. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Must be included in calculations. CAYMAN DANGER (8) can feature with the right run.
